---
export const prerender = true;

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="入选标准 · 互联网奇观 · 人物档案馆">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>入 选 标 准</h1>
      <div class="sub">评 价 体 系</div>
      <div class="desc">为什么是他/她？凭什么入馆？<br />这里有一套标准，但不迷信标准。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">

      <!-- 总纲 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">△</span>总纲</div>
        <p class="no-indent" style="font-size:12px;color:#8a7a6a;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:2.4">
          这里没有网红，只有在围观与挣扎中，被时代重力碾成的命运标本。
        </p>
        <div class="quote-block">
          <em>❝</em>
          "互联网奇观"不等同于"网红"。<br />
          奇观是时代的切片——一个人被卷入或主动制造的文化现象，其存在本身就揭示了互联网时代的某种本质。
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 壹 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">壹</span>核心定义</div>
        <p><strong style="color:#c0a070;font-weight:400">互联网奇观</strong>是指在互联网上形成的、同时具备以下全部特征的公众人物或群体现象：</p>
        <div class="criteria-grid">
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name">现象级</div><div class="ci-desc">跨越圈层，形成广泛社会讨论</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name">不可复制</div><div class="ci-desc">其走红路径无法被刻意模仿</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name">时代标本性</div><div class="ci-desc">承载着某个时期的社会情绪或文化矛盾</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name">叙事完整性</div><div class="ci-desc">有起承转合，构成一个可供讲述的故事</div></div>
        </div>
        <p>一个合格的奇观人物，其存在本身就值得被叙述——不是因为流量，而是因为象征意义。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 贰 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">贰</span>六维评价体系</div>
        <p>每个候选人物按六个维度评分，满分 <strong style="color:#c0a070;font-weight:400">60</strong> 分。准入线 <strong style="color:#c0a070;font-weight:400">36</strong> 分。</p>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">一 · 国民度 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">大众知晓程度，不限于核心受众圈。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–3</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">4–6</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">7–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">丁真 9 · 吴京 10</div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">二 · 争议性 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">讨论烈度与持续时长。零争议不构成奇观。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–2</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">3–5</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">6–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">三和大神 7 · 范小勤 8</div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">三 · 荒诞性 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">离奇、意外、反常识。荒诞是奇观的核心美学。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–2</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">3–5</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">6–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">王伟恒 8 · 良子 8</div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">四 · 时代切片性 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">能否作为某个时代节点的文化锚点。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–2</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">3–5</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">6–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">三和大神 10（注脚一个时代）</div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">五 · 叙事弧光 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">故事的起承转合，是否有"剧本感"。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–2</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">3–5</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">6–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">张雪峰 9 · 范小勤 9</div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-box">
          <div class="criteria-header">六 · 互联网原生性 <span class="dim-light">0–10</span></div>
          <p class="criteria-intro">这个人的名气和现象靠互联网到什么程度。</p>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">0–2</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">3–5</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:35%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">6–8</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-row"><span class="sr-label">9–10</span><div class="sr-bar"><div class="sr-fill high" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="score-notes">丁真 9（7 秒撑起全部）· 吴京 1</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 叁 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">叁</span>否决条件</div>
        <p>具备以下任意一项，即使六维评分达标也不收录：</p>
        <div class="criteria-grid">
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name" style="color:#7a5a4a">纯营销产物</div><div class="ci-desc">MCN 按公式批量生产的达人，缺乏不可复制性</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name" style="color:#7a5a4a">纯猎奇消费</div><div class="ci-desc">单纯消费身体缺陷或苦难，不承载文化意义</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name" style="color:#7a5a4a">信息不确</div><div class="ci-desc">核心事实模糊，无法构建可信叙事</div></div>
          <div class="criteria-item"><div class="ci-name" style="color:#7a5a4a">运营者本人</div><div class="ci-desc">不收录自己人</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 肆 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">肆</span>收录流程</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;margin:16px 0;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;background:rgba(18,15,13,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(60,45,35,0.25);padding:14px 12px;text-align:center">
            <div style="font-size:20px;color:#5a4a3a;font-family:Georgia,serif">①</div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#7a6a5a;letter-spacing:3px">提名</div>
            <div style="font-size:8px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px">请愿墙 / 发现</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;background:rgba(18,15,13,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(60,45,35,0.25);padding:14px 12px;text-align:center">
            <div style="font-size:20px;color:#5a4a3a;font-family:Georgia,serif">②</div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#7a6a5a;letter-spacing:3px">初审</div>
            <div style="font-size:8px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px">六维评分 ≥36</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;background:rgba(18,15,13,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(60,45,35,0.25);padding:14px 12px;text-align:center">
            <div style="font-size:20px;color:#5a4a3a;font-family:Georgia,serif">③</div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#7a6a5a;letter-spacing:3px">归档</div>
            <div style="font-size:8px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px">事实核查 + 写作</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;background:rgba(18,15,13,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(60,45,35,0.25);padding:14px 12px;text-align:center">
            <div style="font-size:20px;color:#5a4a3a;font-family:Georgia,serif">④</div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;color:#7a6a5a;letter-spacing:3px">入库</div>
            <div style="font-size:8px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px">上线档案馆</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 伍 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">伍</span>现有馆藏评分</div>
        <div style="overflow-x:auto">
        <table class="score-table">
          <thead><tr>
            <th style="text-align:left;padding-left:12px">人物</th><th>国民度</th><th>争议性</th><th>荒诞性</th><th>时代切片</th><th>叙事弧光</th><th>互联网原生</th><th>总分</th>
          </tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>丁真</td><td>9</td><td>8</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>7</td><td>9</td><td>48</td></tr>
            <tr><td>范小勤</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>8</td><td>8</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>46</td></tr>
            <tr><td>峰哥</td><td>5</td><td>8</td><td>9</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>9</td><td>46</td></tr>
            <tr><td>三和大神</td><td>7</td><td>7</td><td>7</td><td>10</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>46</td></tr>
            <tr><td>张雪峰</td><td>8</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>8</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>46</td></tr>
            <tr><td>良子</td><td>5</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>5</td><td>8</td><td>8</td><td>41</td></tr>
            <tr><td>王伟恒</td><td>4</td><td>7</td><td>8</td><td>6</td><td>6</td><td>7</td><td>38</td></tr>
            <tr><td>吴京</td><td>10</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td>35</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:10px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:8px">吴京 35 分，低于准入线。收录基于"战狼"作为文化符号的不可绕开性，属特批入库。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 陆 -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="s-h"><span class="num">陆</span>终审原则</div>
        <div class="quote-block" style="border-left-color:rgba(80,65,50,0.6);background:rgba(22,18,14,0.4)">
          <em>❝</em>
          <p style="text-indent:0;font-size:13px;color:#b8a890;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:2">
            如果这个人不存在，<br />
            互联网的这段历史是不是就少了点什么？
          </p>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:10px;color:#5a4a3a;letter-spacing:4px;line-height:2">
            <span style="color:#7a6a5a">合格</span> 少了点精彩。<br />
            <span style="color:#7a6a5a">优秀</span> 少了块拼图。<br />
            <span class="dim">不入</span> 少了谁都一样。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:4px">
        <a class="back-link" href="/">返回档案馆</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <span style="opacity:.4">🦞 麻辣小龙虾 · 标准随时修订</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .wrap{
    max-width:820px;margin:48px auto;position:relative;z-index:2;
    background:linear-gradient(175deg,rgba(16,13,10,0.88) 0%,rgba(10,8,6,0.92) 100%);
    border: 3px double rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.25);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(80,65,50,0.1),
      0 0 0 2px rgba(12,10,8,0.7),
      0 10px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
      inset 0 0 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    padding:0 0 1px 0
  }
  .hero{
    padding:72px 30px 40px;text-align:center;position:relative;
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.18)
  }
  .hero::after{
    content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-1px;left:32px;right:32px;height:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(197,168,128,0.2) 10%,rgba(197,168,128,0.1) 50%,rgba(197,168,128,0.2) 90%,transparent)
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:40px;font-weight:400;color:#e6dfd3;letter-spacing:16px;line-height:1.3;
    text-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 0 60px rgba(197,168,128,0.06);
    font-family:'ZCOOL XiaoWei','Noto Serif SC',serif;font-weight:900
  }
  .hero .sub{font-size:10px;color:#8a7a6a;margin-top:12px;letter-spacing:8px;font-weight:300}
  .hero .sub::before,.hero .sub::after{content:'◆';font-size:4px;color:#c5a880;margin:0 12px;vertical-align:middle;opacity:.4}
  .hero .desc{font-size:12px;color:#9a8a7a;max-width:520px;margin:20px auto 0;line-height:2.2;font-weight:300}
  .content{padding:40px 36px 48px}
  .content .section{margin-bottom:36px;position:relative}
  .content .s-h{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#c5a880;letter-spacing:8px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .content .s-h .num{color:#7a6a5a;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;margin-right:8px}
  .content .s-h::after{content:'';display:block;width:40px;height:1px;background:rgba(197,168,128,0.35);margin-top:8px}
  .content p{font-size:14px;color:#bcae9e;margin-bottom:12px;text-indent:2em;letter-spacing:.5px;line-height:2.0}
  .content p.no-indent{text-indent:0}
  .quote-block{
    margin:20px 0 24px;padding:20px 24px;
    background:rgba(13,11,9,0.5);border-left:2px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.3);
    font-size:12px;color:#9a8a7a;letter-spacing:2px;line-height:2.2
  }
  .quote-block em{font-style:normal;color:#c5a880;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:4px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px}
  .criteria-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin:16px 0 20px}
  .criteria-item{background:rgba(13,11,9,0.35);border:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.15);padding:16px 18px}
  .criteria-item .ci-name{font-size:13px;color:#c5a880;letter-spacing:6px;margin-bottom:4px}
  .criteria-item .ci-desc{font-size:11px;color:#8a7a6a;letter-spacing:2px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300}
  .score-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:11px}
  .score-table th{background:rgba(13,11,9,0.6);color:#8a7a6a;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:3px;padding:8px 6px;border:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.2);text-align:center}
  .score-table td{padding:7px 6px;border:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.15);text-align:center;color:#a89a8a;letter-spacing:1px}
  .score-table td:first-child{color:#c5a880;letter-spacing:3px;text-align:left;padding-left:12px}
  .score-table td:last-child{color:#e6dfd3;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;font-family:'Times New Roman',Georgia,serif}
  
  .criteria-box {
    margin:20px 0;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(13,11,9,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.15)
  }
  .criteria-header {
    font-size:14px;color:#c5a880;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:8px
  }
  .criteria-intro {
    font-size:11px;color:#9a8a7a;text-indent:0;margin-bottom:8px
  }
  .score-notes {
    font-size:10px;color:#6a5a4a;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:6px
  }
  .score-row{display:flex;align-items:center;margin:8px 0;font-size:11px;gap:10px}
  .score-row .sr-label{width:60px;color:#8a7a6a;letter-spacing:3px;flex-shrink:0}
  .score-row .sr-bar{flex:1;height:6px;background:rgba(13,11,9,0.6);position:relative}
  .score-row .sr-fill{height:100%;background:rgba(197,168,128,0.15);transition:width .5s}
  .score-row .sr-fill.high{background:rgba(197,168,128,0.35)}
  .dim{color:#6a5a4a}
  .dim-light{color:#7a6a5a;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px}
  
  .back-link{
    display:inline-block;margin-top:24px;font-size:10px;color:#8a7a6a;
    text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:4px;transition:color .3s;font-weight:400;
    border:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.2);padding:6px 14px;background:rgba(13,11,9,0.5)
  }
  .back-link:hover{color:#c5a880;border-color:rgba(197,168,128,0.4)}
  .back-link::before{content:'← '}
  
  .footer{
    padding:40px 30px 44px;text-align:center;font-size:8px;color:#5a4a3a;
    letter-spacing:3px;line-height:2.4;font-weight:300;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(197,168,128,0.15);position:relative
  }
  .footer::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:-1px;left:32px;right:32px;height:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(197,168,128,0.15) 10%,rgba(197,168,128,0.08) 50%,rgba(197,168,128,0.15) 90%,transparent)
  }
  
  @media(max-width:640px){
    .wrap{margin:10px 6px}
    .hero{padding:40px 16px 28px}
    .hero h1{font-size:26px;letter-spacing:10px}
    .hero .sub::before,.hero .sub::after{display:none}
    .content{padding:24px 16px}
    .criteria-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .score-table{font-size:9px}
    .score-table td, .score-table th{padding:5px 3px}
  }
</style>
